{"tid":2137882,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"許章潤與湯家驊 — 古德明","createTime":"2020-08-03T09:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T09:03:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40259a0ffa4b942afbd4839d188c47948b9a72c7","tid":2137882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:03:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/NHI6Y2LEAFD5ROC7LY3GAHIZRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2FNHI6Y2LEAFD5ROC7LY3GAHIZRA%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=bd18266b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2FNHI6Y2LEAFD5ROC7LY3GAHIZRA%2F&h=7cb3aa9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/NHI6Y2LEAFD5ROC7LY3GAHIZRA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n許章潤與湯家驊 &mdash; 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5lF1mZnbccXwOLiIkbmCA4WBmjg=/593x358/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LEI2THOP5VCQTMX52BZ3FBZSZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5lF1mZnbccXwOLiIkbmCA4WBmjg%3D%2F593x358%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLEI2THOP5VCQTMX52BZ3FBZSZY.jpg&h=1316e029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京清華大學法律學教授許章潤。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n許章潤違反新時代教師守則，。。。。。。。。。。。。。一日不卸。」這當然是新時代不容許的。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。他一被清華革職，即有五百多位清華校友為之張羅，籌得十萬元生活費，於此或可見其敗壞之道德。<br />\n<br />\n許章潤令人想起新時代香港御用大律師湯家驊。兩人都是法律界中人，一個是中共階下囚，身披嫖娼罪名，生計無着；一個是中共座上客，身無嫖娼罪名，富且貴焉。兩人可以說是過去七十年中國知識分子的縮影。千秋芳臭，一瞬枯榮，知所選擇者能有幾人。"}]}